Conv2d Pruning

{% raw %}
{% endraw %}

A Conv2d layer possess a 4d-tensor as weights. This means that there exist many ways of removing blocks from it.

0-D blocks

The most simple way is to remove individual weights, i.e. remove 0-dimension blocks

{% raw %} 
get_pruned_conv(0)
{% endraw %}
